(16000, '_transient_create-listing_f662641f0602d88c2a91_20', 'a:7:{s:13:\"checkout_type\";s:14:\"create-listing\";s:10:\"listing_id\";i:644;s:11:\"category_id\";s:2:\"88\";s:7:\"form_id\";s:1:\"1\";s:12:\"complete_url\";s:84:\"http://savemari.co.za/create-listing-2/?step=order-summary&hash=f662641f0602d88c2a91\";s:10:\"cancel_url\";s:85:\"http://savemari.co.za/create-listing-2/?step=gateway-select&hash=f662641f0602d88c2a91\";s:13:\"posted_fields\";a:22:{s:10:\"ad_pack_id\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"featured_ad\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"app_attach_id\";a:1:{i:0;s:3:\"645\";}s:16:\"app_attach_title\";a:1:{i:0;s:2:\"n1\";}s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"cp_price\";s:6:\"250000\";s:11:\"cp_currency\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:47:\"5D Cinema/Theatre 6 Seater Business Oppertunity\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:4096:\"Business Opportunity for sale. We are selling one of our 5D theatres. Currently it is 4 years old. There is no defects and the product is working optimal. The cost include transport to any location in South Africa and also include the setup of the 5D. There is 45 movies included with the sale.\r\n\r\nWhat is 5D cinema?\r\n5D cinema is a perfect combination of 3D images and cinema motion effects produced by the special equipment which can be felt with the human perceptive organs. The viewer becomes totally involved in what is happening on the screen and can feel the movements and happenings on the screen like rays of sun, wind blowing, and humid air of the ocean breeze etc. In cases of 5D theatres, seats move in synchronization with motion in the movie thus providing immersive experience to the audiences. The theatre is equipped with motion chairs which can move in at least six directional movements like left-right tilts; forward-backward tilts and up-down movements. These theatres use specialized software to produce multiple special effects and very beautifully represent an excellent integration of 3D technology, audio, motion and synchronization. The invention of 5d cinema allowed us to plunge in the world of virtual reality, this enabling you become totally involved in what is happening on the screen.\r\n5D dynamic seats\r\nThe 5D motion chairs are special chairs equipped with high technology features to produce different kinds of movements like up and down, left and right, tumbling action front and back, simulation pitch, roll, lift movement, tumbling run, flight, etc., forward suspended, fall, up to see, rise etc. to give a realistic feel of the movie.\r\n5D special effects system\r\n5D special effects: Bubble, chair movement, lightning, rain, snow, leg sweep, wind and water spray. The seats usually moves according to the film story, the cinema contains special effects which are controlled by the computer. The combination of the movie plot and special effects in the 5D movies, makes the viewer feel the scene very close and gain an all-around experience from your vision, hearing, touching and takes you into a movie environment which can be felt as a real world. This is the 5D Cinema which is now very popular around the world.\r\n5D special screen\r\nFrom the visual sense the screen structure of 5D cinema is a that of a stereoscopic image. The screen is silver oxided to improve the 3D experience and to reduce ghosting of the movie. The aspect ratio of the screen is 16:9,and it can widely expand the scope of movement for 3D objects and horizon, get rid of the constraint of plane sight and make the movie space more resemble that of real space. It can generate modes of motion such as crossing and surround images. (it’s different from the “flat video” – which limits not only the audience’s visual angle, but also the movement direction of the objects.)\r\n5D Projectors system\r\nDuel high resolution projectors are used to make viewers take part in the films, you are not only viewers but also participant.\r\n5D Acoustic audio system\r\nThe 5D cinema sound system is made up of multi channel sound system. The sound enhance the environmental effects. The cabin is enclosed in sound proofing acoustic foam to greatly reduce sound outside the cabin.\r\n5D stereo-glasses\r\nFor viewers to enjoy stereoscopic motion picture, polarized glasses is used (the “stereo glasses”)for watching stereoscopic motion picture. It takes different movie images from viewer’s left eye and right eye, so that the image reflected in the human brain is a 3D image, thereby creating an immersed scene of a three-dimensional visual space.\r\n5D Computer Control System\r\nTo make sure that the above elements are achieved a computer is needed to control all the functions. The computer is the core of the 5D cinema. Software and programs are used to make sure that every function takes place where and when it is needed. The movie is pre- programed for the computer and then the computer set the exact time when to execute the projection of sound, when to produce special effects e.t.c.\";s:10:\"tags_input\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"cp_street\";s:9:\"cape town\";s:7:\"cp_city\";s:9:\"cape town\";s:8:\"cp_state\";s:16:\"The Western Cape\";s:10:\"cp_country\";s:12:\"South Africa\";s:16:\"cp_cpphonenumber\";s:10:\"0844252324\";s:3:\"fid\";s:1:\"1\";s:3:\"cat\";s:2:\"88\";s:17:\"cp_sys_ad_conf_id\";s:16:\"17058b19300f20a0\";s:13:\"cp_sys_userIP\";s:13:\"90.217.215.31\";s:18:\"cp_sys_ad_duration\";s:2:\"90\";s:20:\"cp_sys_total_ad_cost\";i:0;}}', 'no'),
