ocs.appthemes.com/vantage/vantage-version-1-4/\">release notes</a> to see all the details. Make sure you&#8217;ve got the latest version of our <a href=\"http://www.appthemes.com/blog/new-plugin-to-keep-your-themes-healthy/\">updater plugin</a> to ensure a smooth upgrade process.</p>\n<p>Clipper 1.6 is in testing now. We should have it ready for release next week. JobRoller, ClassiPress, and HireBee are next on the schedule.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s all for now. Have a great weekend!</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=8RYkVWV01DM:UGD3rLe7JFM:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/appthemes/~4/8RYkVWV01DM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.appthemes.com/blog/website-redesign-and-more/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\