(76, 1, '2015-05-05 01:36:27', '2015-05-04 23:36:27', '<h1><u><b>WHAT SAVEMARI BRINGS TO YOUR BUSINESS</b></u></h1>\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Increase Customers</strong></span>\r\n\r\nMost business have local popularity, but what about potential customers outside their city or country?  At www.savemari.co.za  ,we can help you generate more customers. Not just outside your city,or province but worldwide.We offers a global community to your business. With so many South African world wide, they are always looking for information, business , products in South Africa . With are website, your business, services and products will be visible to all SOUTH AFRICANS around the world.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>Accessibility</b></span>\r\nWell, you don’t have to close the doors of your website or keep checking weather your markerting team is doing their  job.With www.savemari.co.za , you can check how many people viewed your advert, who are they sharing it with etc.  An on-line  advert can be visited any-time of the day or night. People will look AT your business world wide instead of you seating down  and waiting  for your local customers, its because  www.savemari.co.za  its more accessible. Just make sure you post enough information about your products and services.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>Fresh</b></span>\r\n\r\nSmart business owners always create new adverts  for their company. Having  to post fresh advert overtime will keep your customers attracted to you and accredit to do business with you\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>Links</b></span>\r\nLinks are very important to viral marketing. If you have many sites linking to you, it is like spreading the word about your company all around the world. If you have a good advert(s) with good content , attractive pictures and related to information, products or services, people are more likely to link your post to theirs like, Facebook, twitter, and many more social media. This means they recognize your products as valuable.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>Better Relationship</b></span>\r\nHaving an account @ www.savemari.co.za  will build better relationships with your customers. You can send messages instantly to your customers through email services. Also, your customers can review your products online and can also leave feedback for you and your business. This is essential for <a href=\"http://dogulindigital.com.au/social-media-networking-for-businesses/\" target=\"_blank\">building a good relationship</a> with them.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>Increase Sales</b></span>\r\nIf you are a business owner, more visitors  leads to more potential sales. That’s how your advert(s) at www.savemari.co.za  help you. You can drive more people to your company by consistently updating and promoting the contents of your advert(s). The more informative your advert(s) is, the greater the possibility of increasing your sales.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>Opportunity</b></span>\r\n\r\nOur  website gives you the opportunity to prove your credibility. You have to tell your customers why you deserve their trust through our website. This will earn  you positive feedback for your service and products on you advert(s). Also, our website serves as a place for a potential investor to explore what your business is about and what it can do in the future.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>Long Term Clients</b></span>\r\nWhat do you think is the difference between client and a customer? Well, a customer is the one who walks in and buys something and that’s it. A client is your regular customer. He is buying your products or services daily or contractually. Having your business on our website gives you a chance to gain more clients that can help your business grow.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Knowledge Base', '', 'publish', 'closed', 