(111, 10, '2015-08-10 20:32:32', '2015-08-10 18:32:32', '<strong>CAPE TOWN TRIKE TOURS is the only trike tour operator in Cape Town. Come and experience the stunning scenery that only Cape Town can offer, from the back of this fully imported, German built trike...the only one of its kind in South Africa. The trike seats two passengers and helmets are supplied. All tours are conducted by a licensed and registered tour guide.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>We offer four set tours but we will customize any tour according to your wishes.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>We offer:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>* Cape Point &amp; peninsula tour...full day.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>* Whale Route &amp; Hermanus tour...full day.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>* Cape Winelands tour...full day and includes two wine tastings.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>* Sunset tour...approx. 2.5 hours and includes finger snacks and a bottle of sparkling wine. This tour can be done on either Signal Hill or at an additional cost, to Chapmans peak.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>We are also available for weddings and matric functions.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Check out our website for more information regarding our tours and prices on <a href=\"http://www.capetriketours.co.za/\">www.capetriketours.co.za</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>AN EXPERIENCE YOU WILL NEVER FORGET!!!</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'CAPE TOWN TRIKE TOURS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'cape-town-trike-tours', '', '', '2016-02-14 01:16:38', '2016-02-13 23:16:38', 'CAPE TOWN TRIKE TOURS, CAPE TOWN TRIKE TOURS is the only trike tour operator in Cape Town. Come and experience the stunning scenery that only Cape Town can offer, from the back of this fully imported, German built trike...the only one of its kind in South Africa. The trike seats two passengers and helmets are supplied. All tours are conducted by a licensed and registered tour guide. We offer four set tours but we will customize any tour according to your wishes. We offer: * Cape Point &amp; peninsula tour...