(130, 9, '2015-09-19 01:05:10', '2015-09-18 23:05:10', '<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">Very successfull Night Club/pub on offer on busy strip - Brooklyn/Rugby/Ysterplaat area</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">The business has existed in its current guise and branding since 2012, and for many years before as a Sports Bar. Very well established in the area with a very loyal local clientele keeping the weekday trade turning over steadily.</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">The last year has seen the business undergo a massive revival - new ownership has breathed new life into it, and it is currently the premier night-time party spot in the entire area, and gaining popularity every week, with people traveling from all over the Peninsula to come and enjoy themselves.</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">With state-of-the-art sound and lighting installed on the dance floor and very versatile resident DJs, we are able to cater for, and accommodate a very wide clientele, and it reflects in our crowds on weekend club nights - we have patrons of all ages, and completely culturally diverse.</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">Karaoke currently offered on Wednesdays and Sundays - soon to be offered in the bar area every week night.\r\nDance floor open on Thursday, Friday and Saturday.</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">We run a very tight ship with strict security and as a result, we have become known as a safe and secure party spot for everyone.</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">Loyal and reliable staff, the majority of them has been around for several years.</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">Kitchen currently outsourced to a local NPO, which runs it Friday to Sunday nights. Opportunity exists to expand the kitchen offering, or take it back in-house.\r\nSite has been earmarked as a gambling site, and negotiations have been started.</p>\r\n<p class=\"listing-paragraph\">Please contact for further details, photos, asset list etc.</p>', 'bar club for sale', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'bar-club-for-sale', '', '', '2015-09-19 01:05:10', '2015-09-18 23:05:10', 'bar club for sale, Very successfull Night Club/pub on offer on busy strip - Brooklyn/Rugby/Ysterplaat area The business has existed in its current guise and branding since 2012, and for many years before as a Sports Bar. Very well established in the area with a very loyal local clientele keeping the weekday trade turning over steadily. The last year has seen the business undergo a massive revival - new ownership has breathed new life into it, and it is currently the premier night-time party spot in the entire area, and gaining popularity every week, with people traveling from all over the Peninsula to come and enjoy themselves. With state-of-the-art sound and lighting installed on the dance floor and very versatile resident DJs, we are able to cater for, and accommodate a very wide clientele, and it reflects in our crowds on weekend club nights - we have patrons of all ages, and completely culturally diverse. Karaoke currently offered on Wednesdays and Sundays - soon to be offered in the bar area every week night. Dance floor open on Thursday, Friday and Saturday. We run a very tight ship with strict security and as a result, we have become known as a safe and secure party spot for everyone. Loyal and reliable staff, the majority of them has been around for several years. Kitchen currently outsourced to a local NPO, which runs it Friday to Sunday nights. Opportunity exists to expand the kitchen offering, or take it back in-house. Site has been earmarked as a gambling site, and negotiations have been started. Please contact for further details, photos, asset list etc., 120000, warren park hights, cape town, The Western Cape, South Africa, 40855fc88088a18c, Accounting And Taxation', 0, 'http://savemari.co.za/?post_type=ad_listing&#038;p=130', 0, 'ad_listing', '', 0),
