(161, 12, '2015-09-22 23:19:52', '2015-09-22 21:19:52', '<ul class=\"selMenu\">\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"name\">Location</span>\r\n<div class=\"location\"><a href=\"http://www.gumtree.co.za/s-barkly-west/v1l3100486p1\">Barkly West</a>, <a href=\"http://www.gumtree.co.za/s-northern-cape/v1l3100213p1\">Northern Cape</a></div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">For Rent By</span> <span class=\"value\">Agency</span></div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">Minimum Nights</span> <span class=\"value\">1</span></div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">Sleeps</span> <span class=\"value\">6</span></div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">Dwelling Type</span> <span class=\"value\">Farm</span></div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">Bedrooms (#)</span> <span class=\"value\">3 bedrooms</span></div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">Bathrooms (#)</span> <span class=\"value\">3 bathrooms</span></div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">Smoking</span> <span class=\"value\">No</span></div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"attribute\"><span class=\"name\">Pet Friendly</span> <span class=\"value\">No</span></div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"description\">\r\n\r\nCome and experience the tranquillity and hospitality of the Northern Cape at Die Olyfhuis (The Olive House) , an exclusive guest house on the Farm Holsdam. The farm, situated five kilometres from Barkly West and 39 kilometres from Kimberley, is the perfect location to relax and de-stress. Kenne and Joy, owners of both Holsdam and Die Olyfhuis, are ready to welcome you to their bit of paradise.\r\n\r\nDie Olyfhuis is a luxurious rustic guest house that has been decorated with a Boere-French flair, surrounded by Mission olive trees. Every bedroom has hand-crafted natural wood furniture\r\n\r\nCome and enjoy the exclusivity and privacy of the three luxurious en-suite double bedrooms. Each room was individually decorated by an interior designer to not only offer ultimate comfort, but also blend with the farm’s peaceful and natural surroundings. DStv and Wi-Fi internet are provided in all rooms.\r\n\r\nAt Die Olyfhuis you have the opportunity to experience how restful and rejuvenating farm-life can be. You can take long walks and explore the tranquil surroundings. Birdwatchers will find a bit of paradise with 45 different bird species and two dams where they can be spotted. For those who wish to be a bit more active, we have an established walking trail and a mountain bike route.\r\n\r\nBreakfast is included with your stay at Die Olyfhuis. Dinner, BBQ and picnic baskets are available by arrangement.\r\n\r\n<b>Game Viewing</b> There are beautiful game farms in the area for game drives.\r\n\r\n<b>Bird Watching</b> Birdwatchers will find a bit of paradise with 45 different bird species and two dams where they can be spotted\r\n\r\n<b>Hiking Trails</b> At Die Olyfhuis you have the opportunity to experience how restful and rejuvenating farm-life can be. You can take long walks and explore the tranquil surroundings. For those who wish to be a bit more active, we have an established walking trail and a mountain bike route (60 km)\r\n\r\n<b>Other Activities</b> Kimberley is 42 km from the farm where there are lots of interesting things to so - the Big Hole, historical; buildings, golf course and the Flamingo casino\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Barkley West – Kimberley – Exclusive Olyfhuis Guest House - luxurious &amp; rustic', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'barkley-west-kimberley-exclusive-olyfhuis-guest-house-luxurious-rustic', '', '', '2015-09-22 23:19:52', '2015-09-22 21:19:52', 'Barkley West – Kimberley – Exclusive Olyfhuis Guest House - luxurious &amp; rustic, Location Barkly West, Northern Cape For Rent By Agency Minimum Nights 1 Sleeps 6 Dwelling Type Farm Bedro