eded. The movie is pre- programed for the computer and then the computer set the exact time when to execute the projection of sound, when to produce special effects e.t.c.', '5D Cinema/Theatre 6 Seater Business Oppertunity', '', 'pending', 'closed', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2017-02-25 16:22:24', '2017-02-25 14:22:24', '5D Cinema/Theatre 6 Seater Business Oppertunity, Business Opportunity for sale. We are selling one of our 5D theatres. Currently it is 4 years old. There is no defects and the product is working optimal. The cost include transport to any location in South Africa and also include the setup of the 5D. There is 45 movies included with the sale. What is 5D cinema? 5D cinema is a perfect combination of 3D images and cinema motion effects produced by the special equipment which can be felt with the human perceptive organs. The viewer becomes totally involved in what is happening on the screen and can feel the movements and happenings on the screen like rays of sun, wind blowing, and humid air of the ocean breeze etc. In cases of 5D theatres, seats move in synchronization with motion in the movie thus providing immersive experience to the audiences. The theatre is equipped with motion chairs which can move in at least six directional movements like left-right tilts; forward-backward tilts and up-down movements. These theatres use specialized software to produce multiple special effects and very beautifully represent an excellent integration of 3D technology, audio, motion and synchronization. The invention of 5d cinema allowed us to plunge in the world of virtual reality, this enabling you become totally involved in what is happening on the screen. 5D dynamic seats The 5D motion chairs are special chairs equipped with high technology features to produce different kinds of movements like up and down, left and right, tumbling action front and back, simulation pitch, roll, lift movement, tumbling run, flight, etc., forward suspended, fall, up to see, rise etc. 